---
// Dresscode.astro
---

<section class="hp-dresscode-section">
    <!-- Icono Sombrero Seleccionador / Magia -->
    <i class="ph-thin ph-sparkle hp-dresscode-icon hp-levitate"></i>
    <h2 class="hp-dresscode-title">Atuendo Requerido</h2>
    <p class="hp-dresscode-text">
        Túnicas de gala, tu uniforme de la casa, o tu mejor cosplay de
        películas. No se permiten prendas Muggles aburridas.<br />
        <span class="hp-dresscode-highlight"
            >¡Vístete para impresionar o te lanzaremos un maleficio!</span
        >
    </p>
</section>

<style>
    .hp-dresscode-section {
        padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hp-dresscode-icon {
        font-size: 2.25rem; /* 36px */
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-ink-red);
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .hp-dresscode-title {
        font-family: var(--font-magic);
        font-size: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-ink);
    }

    .hp-dresscode-text {
        color: var(--color-ink-light);
        line-height: 1.625;
        font-weight: 600;
        max-width: 32rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hp-dresscode-highlight {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--color-ink-red);
        margin-top: 1rem;
        display: block;
    }
</style>
